myth hads it that their is a maze in a park that if you stay there til midnight you'll be trapped forever.
john try to see if the myth is true, so one day he goes into that parks maze, and stood there til midnight,
only to find it to be true. John trys to get out as soon as he can only to fall in vain.
john finds himself trapped in a maze, he try to get out by following a path and a door is locked blocking his path, 
only to open to whoever could solve its puzzle, can you solve all the puzzles, and escape?
